text: Disillusioned tribalism disguised as sophistication. Lots of that about.
Throwing a tantrum to distract from the fact that my tribe sucks in particular moment.

... "... and your candidate is a crude, brutal, thug."
"Yes."
... Probably nowhere near crude and brutal enough for what we need, but it's a start.
You don't think it's at all  weird that the moment the regime you've been criticizing begins to crumble you get incredibly prickly and defensive? ...
... "Why won't anyone listen to me respectfully about Lech Walesa also being an asshole?"
